caption.p: Kaplan-Meier survival curves of eleven key lncRNAs related to overall survival (OS). LINC02038 ( a) and AC104823.1 ( b) were positively correlated with OS. MIR4435-2HG ( c), ELFN1-AS1 ( d), NKILA ( e), AFAP1-AS1 ( f), AL591845.1 ( g), AL355987.4 ( h), AL354836.1 ( i), AC005520.2 ( j), and AC245884.8 ( k) were negatively correlated with OS. The red lines represent the high expression groups, and the blue lines represent the low expression groups
